{"tid":356770,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 椒鹽雞軟骨","createTime":"2017-08-12T10:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T09:23:17.000Z","uid":74981,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cd002ce4c24c4051df388cbd0da7f96bd7ffc4","tid":356770,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s11.postimg.org/vj5gea7b7/20170812_174354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs11.postimg.org%2Fvj5gea7b7%2F20170812_174354.jpg&h=059a21bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fNWpQmMzN1U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfNWpQmMzN1U&d=20zEhBqoAHY0DZ7WuRoCzwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a76324c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fNWpQmMzN1U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n雞軟骨約30粒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>調味:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n辣椒2條切粒<br />\n<br />\n炸蒜1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n沙薑粉大半茶匙<br />\n<br />\n胡椒鹽少許<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法概述:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 雞軟骨洗淨抹乾上粉, 粉唔好太多唔好太少, 多餘既粉用隔&quot;西&quot;&quot;西&quot;番出黎.<br />\n<br />\n2. 油7成熱落雞軟骨, 慢火炸, 如覺得油溫太熱就熄火一陣先開慢火, 炸果時因為會痴埋一舊, 儘量用獲剷分番開佢地.<br />\n<br />\n3. 炸一陣, 開大火炸一陣, 扯番D油出黎, 隔油上碟.<br />\n<br />\n4. 倒剩少少油, 清左D污糟野, 開中小火, 爆香辣椒, 炸蒜, 落番D雞軟骨, 落沙薑粉, 胡椒鹽炒勻, 完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 切記, 雞軟骨不能炸過火, 否則會硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e42a2b661d222eae4a7677ca16e672531eaa3f","tid":356770,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a0ad3c8b5d8c10062498255da8c50b03099c5","tid":356770,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n查查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957ac3dfca43f5256ac84eefd0efa5ae88bd707d","tid":356770,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"屌炸天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dfe41a653bc81b6a7597bfddffbb80823d7784","tid":356770,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18310db45ec1655d230e8bf22a7e71c37b5ebd9","tid":356770,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌炸天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衲dee<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2fd88028e4e0476bd9a1c5dd15f7299ae49530","tid":356770,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05cd6d73a0c91f9c84291bea0330d07ab3a853c","tid":356770,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"好正，送酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0738db805ed28e85fa4f07fa4c2c0f870c974345","tid":356770,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正，送酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一碟起碼送兩支大啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3799ed3f1d31800bdc87e0e2e42e7581d27f8d","tid":356770,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20